                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Department’s press release of October 4, 1950, announcing that the United
                    Nations Command in Korea had accepted Colombia’s offer (made September 18) of a
                    manned frigate, appears in the Department of State <hi rend="italic"
                        >Bulletin</hi>, October 16, 1950, page 606.</p>
                <p>On November 14 the Colombian Government offered an infantry battalion for Korean
                    duty (<hi rend="italic">ibid</hi>., November 27, 1950, page 870.) Pertinent
                    documentation is scheduled for publication in volume I.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
